OL,3,CHillsborough Law to prevent cover-ups
OL,4,C'must be all or nothing', campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Establishing a duty of candour could
OL,8,Fprevent this, help us learn from
OL,9,Ffailures and ensure bereaved and
OL,10,Fsurvivors are properly supported. This
OL,11,Fis why a Hillsborough Law is so
OL,12,Furgent."
OL,14,FLobby Akinnola from CBFFJ, whose
OL,15,Ffather died in the pandemic, said:
OL,16,F"Those bereaved by Covid have seen
OL,17,Ffirst-hand how easily the truth is
OL,18,Fdelayed, diluted or denied.
